---
title: Chermoula Salmon & Leafy Garlic Rice with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Seared pink salmon has got to be the fanciest fish in the sea, elegant and fresh. Tonight, we’ve tossed it in our chermoula-spice blend, lending a bright and zesty flavour. Laid atop a bed of leafy garlic rice with a rainbow of roast veg, this simple and flavourful meal allows the salmon to shine!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
